text: Omosarotes singularis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Pascoe in 1860. It is known from Costa Rica, Brazil, Panama.BioLib.cz - Omosarotes singularis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Cyrtinini Category:Beetles described in 1860
